     C* EXCPT: write E-record RLINE per input record
     FXDATA   IP  F    80              DISK
     FXOUT    O   F    132             PRINTER
     IXDATA   AA  01
     I                                     1   2   NNMBR
     C                     EXCPTRLINE
     OXOUT    E  1             RLINE
     O                                 5    'N='
     O                         NMBR    10
